description.narrative: During 2021, UNICEF Venezuela continued building on the work initiated in 2019, ensuring the continuation of strong datacentric programme monitoring mechanisms, including humanitarian performance monitoring (HPM), and enhancing planning processes to ensure alignment with UNICEF’s Annual Work Plan, HRP and HAC.The PM&E team provided guidance, leadership, and relevant information to facilitate programme planning (including the implementing of partner strategy, HACT standards, and capacity building of the CO’s staff and IPs), monitoring (both CO performance and situation of children), evaluation, reporting, and feedback tools for affected populations. | Status:On-track | As-of Date:19/01/2022
